                        <ab type="answer">  MODÈLE. <!--Should this be futher tagged as some sort of category--> — <!--<seg corresp="#francais">-->Verrez<!--</seg>-->, mode indic., temps futur. <lb/>
                        <!--<seg corresp="#francais">-->Taillera<!--</seg>-->, mode indic., temps futur.
